{"tid":2356472,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港台：特朗普籲支持者回家　拜登指襲擊國會是暴動不是抗議","createTime":"2021-01-06T22:57:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T23:45:44.000Z","uid":290404,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"fb2e2a1da970353d059e93c51029756147bdc373","tid":2356472,"uid":290404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T22:57:05.000Z","msg":"美國一批總統特朗普的支持者，闖入國會山莊，導致正進行確認各州選舉人大選投票結果程序的聯席會議，被逼暫停。<br />\n<br />\n示威者與警方爆發激烈衝突，國會內情況混亂，議事廳有玻璃窗被打碎，國會警察要舉槍戒備。報道說警方曾施放催淚彈，有人中槍，亦有其他人受傷。國民警衛軍及聯邦警方奉召到國會控制場面，華盛頓哥倫比亞特區市長鮑澤，下令當地周三傍晚6時起宵禁。<br />\n<br />\n總統特朗普在社交專頁上載片段，重申選舉結果被偷走，又說知道支持者感到痛楚及受傷，但呼籲他們是時候回家。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>總統當選人拜登形容，襲擊國會不是抗議，而是暴動，又指民主是脆弱的， 需要並非醉心於個人權力，而是重視共同利益的領袖，加以維護，呼籲特朗普捍衛憲法，結束國會被圍困的局面。</strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569062-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569062-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=tgCcTb3Ji4LFIEkqsM1g5ivt59O44HeJS3%2BtxtDyp5g%3D&h=3e5d04b4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1569062-20210107.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=175a816f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1569062-20210107.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c44fbf806f241e823ceaced79497c50aba04b4dd","tid":2356472,"uid":155246,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:03:59.000Z","msg":"China Joe啲口吻好撚似隻比卡超"},{"pid":"a129b5451ce90c913ad7176c2d791f2742f4885d","tid":2356472,"uid":300782,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"c44fbf806f241e823ceaced79497c50aba04b4dd","tid":2356472,"uid":155246,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:03:59.000Z","msg":"China Joe啲口吻好撚似隻比卡超"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T23:07:01.000Z","msg":"人有幾千萬票"},{"pid":"42f6a10c2bdcf32a4a6c4ab2477d8e6109cd75c8","tid":2356472,"uid":191926,"like":4,"dislike"